                     <interp inst="t18260914-106-person776" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, and took the prisoner from Mr. Copsey.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in company with a young woman, who took me to the Strand, where I was taken.</p>
